{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"6588bab3-6ebb-4893-93d6-2428c2fbcdee","content":"No existing files found, so I'll provide the solution directly.\n\n## Compiled Bindings in .NET MAUI\n\nTo convert your page, add `x:DataType` to the `ContentPage` element pointing to your ViewModel:\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" ?>\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n        <Entry Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" Placeholder=\"Theme\" />\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n        <Stepper Value=\"{Binding FontSize}\" Minimum=\"8\" Maximum=\"48\" />\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize, StringFormat='Font Size: {0}'}\" />\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\nThe key change is **`x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"`** — this tells the XAML compiler the type of the `BindingContext`, enabling compiled bindings.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\n1. **Enable strict mode** — compiled bindings already emit warnings for invalid property names. To promote these to **errors**, add this to your `.csproj`:\n\n   ```xml\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <WarningsAsErrors>XC0045</WarningsAsErrors>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n   `XC0045` is the diagnostic for binding path issues with `x:DataType`.\n\n2. **Ensure `x:DataType` is set** on every element that uses `{Binding}`. Without it, bindings fall back to reflection (no compile-time checking).\n\n3. **Opt out selectively** — if you need a runtime binding (e.g., in a `DataTemplate` with polymorphism), use `x:DataType=\"\"` to clear the type on that scope.\n\nWith this setup, a typo like `{Binding Thme}` will fail the build instead of silently returning `null` at runtime.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"959c1f7c-0524-49b9-8b0d-142530df4368","outputTokens":561,"requestId":"A85E:21155A:679215:771A31:69FBE1D5"},"id":"b98765bb-442d-439d-9c0d-7650fdb64563","timestamp":"2026-05-07T00:50:41.170Z","parentId":"5f8755e2-8a07-4ac6-8b46-661997224b7d"}
